### 技能数据查看 API 示例
### 这些接口用于查看已爬取的技能数据

### 1. 获取完整的爬取数据 (JSON格式)
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. 获取数据摘要和统计信息
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/summary
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. 按分类获取技能数据 - 热门AI技能
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/category/hotAISkills
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. 按分类获取技能数据 - Skills.sh相关
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/category/skillsShRelated
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. 搜索技能 - 关键词搜索
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?q=ai
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. 搜索技能 - 按作者筛选
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?author=microsoft
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. 搜索技能 - 按星标范围筛选
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?stars_min=10000&stars_max=100000
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. 搜索技能 - 按标签筛选
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?tag=python
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. 组合搜索 - Microsoft的AI相关项目，星标大于1000
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?q=ai&author=microsoft&stars_min=1000
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. 搜索高星标项目
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?stars_min=50000
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. 搜索框架类项目
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?tag=framework
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. 搜索智能体相关项目
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?q=agent
Accept: application/json

###

### 13. 搜索LLM相关项目
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?tag=llm
Accept: application/json

###

### 14. 测试无效分类
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/category/invalid_category
Accept: application/json

###

### 15. 复杂搜索 - Python AI框架，星标1万以上
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/data/search?q=python&tag=ai&stars_min=10000
Accept: application/json

###